import React from 'react'
import * as C from './styles'

const ResumeItem = ({ title }) => {
  return (
    <C.Container>
      <C.Header>
        <C.HeaderTitle>{title}</C.HeaderTitle>
        <Icon />
      </C.Header>
      <C.Total>1000</C.Total>
    </C.Container>
  )
}

export default ResumeItem
